Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Two contiguous landholdings - The Dip (178Ha*) and Swinging Bridge Cottage (46Ha*) offered in one line or as separate assets.

A rural lifestyle opportunity in a desirable location with productive capability; currently operated as a beef and sheep breeding/finishing and irrigated fodder production enterprise.

North-easterly aspect, rising from the Goodradigbee River to undulating hills with panoramic views over the valley and river; much of The Dip is hidden from Nottingham Road, affording privacy.

Quality improved and native pastures plus 22Ha* of K-Line pod irrigation underpinned by a targeted fertiliser program sustain a combined carrying capacity of 1,850DSE*.

Comprehensive operational improvements and three comfortable residences (The Dip homestead, guest cottage and Swinging Bridge Cottage) ensure ease of management and a range of accommodation/rental options.

Extensive frontage to the Goodradigbee River, eight dams and reticulated water system provide adequate water for livestock, irrigation and domestic purposes.

103ML* Goodradigbee River General Security Water Access Licence and 1ML* Stock and Domestic Water Access Licence.

63 kilometres* to Yass, 92 kilometres* to Canberra and 299 kilometres* to M5/M7 intersection near Sydney.

FOR SALE IN ONE LINE OR AS SEPARATE ASSETS BY EXPRESSION OF INTEREST CLOSING THURSDAY 18TH OCTOBER 2018 AT 4.00PM (AEDT)

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Approximately 5,500mᶾ* of predominantly Mountain Gum lumber, ideal for furniture, flooring, architraves and numerous other internal and external uses.

2,863Ha* of grazing land, located in a high rainfall district underpinning a sustainable carrying capacity of 3,000DSE*.

Secure water sources via several permanent springs, nine dams and three semi-permanent creeks.

Total of 19 lots with subdivision potential via four 40Ha* lots.

Cattle yards and machinery shed, abandoned homestead with power and phone connected.

Land and lumber are being offered in one line or as separate assets on a contingent basis.
